<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About the Company - Prime Infra</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/publicapplicant.css">
    <style>
        /* Simple and modern style for announcements */
        .announcements {
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            border-radius: 8px;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto;
        }

        .announcements h2 {
            font-size: 1.8em;
            color: #07ACB9;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .announcement-content {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .announcement-item {
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-size: 1em;
            color: #555;
        }

        .announcement-item .subject {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .announcement-item .timestamp {
            font-size: 0.9em;
            color: #888;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .announcement-item .description {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 1em;
        }

        .announcement-content p.no-announcement {
            text-align: center;
            color: #999;
            font-style: italic;
        }

    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('../partials/publicheader') %>

    <!-- Announcements Window -->
    <section class="announcements">
        <h2>ANNOUNCEMENTS</h2>
        <div class="announcement-content">
            <!-- Dummy announcements for demo purposes -->
            <div class="announcement-item">
                <div class="subject">New Office Opening</div>
                <div class="timestamp">Posted on: September 15, 2024</div>
                <div class="description">We are excited to announce the opening of our new office in Singapore. This expansion will help us better serve our clients in the Asia-Pacific region.</div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="announcement-item">
                <div class="subject">Annual General Meeting</div>
                <div class="timestamp">Posted on: September 10, 2024</div>
                <div class="description">The Annual General Meeting will be held on October 25, 2024. All shareholders are encouraged to attend to review the past year's performance and discuss future plans.</div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="announcement-item">
                <div class="subject">Holiday Schedule</div>
                <div class="timestamp">Posted on: September 5, 2024</div>
                <div class="description">Our offices will be closed from December 24, 2024, to January 2, 2025, for the holidays. We wish you all a joyous holiday season!</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="about-us">
        <div class="purpose-mission">
            <div class="purpose">
                <h2>PURPOSE</h2>
                <p>Better lives and resilient economies, through critical infrastructure.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="mission">
                <h2>MISSION</h2>
                <p>Transforming developing markets around the world by providing them with reliable, resilient, and sustainable infrastructure, carried out through fast and lean management processes, a holistic thinking approach, and a customer-centric mindset.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <h2 class="values-heading">OUR VALUES</h2>
        <div class="values-container">
            <div class="value">
                <h3>VALUE CREATION</h3>
                <p>We create meaningful value by investing in projects that improve the quality of life for our host communities, investing in the development and welfare of our employees, and managing these investments to deliver high returns to our shareholders.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="value">
                <h3>INTEGRITY</h3>
                <p>We are ethical, fair, and transparent in our business practices at every level of our organization while delivering a profitable and sustainable business, and expect similar behavior from our business partners.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="value">
                <h3>PIONEERING</h3>
                <p>We evolve new approaches, explore new methods and ideas, in order to create innovative solutions and deliver lasting impact for the countries in which we operate.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="value">
                <h3>PASSION</h3>
                <p>We live and breathe the work that we do, and seek out colleagues and business partners that share the same deep commitment to our purpose.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</body>
</html>
